com.phunware.core.cme.models

Class Structure

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.phunware.core.cme.models.Structure
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.os.Parcelable

    public class Structure
extends java.lang.Object
implements android.os.Parcelable
    Structure is used to build the structure and hierarchy of data. Each structure item that is defined as an object can also optionally be assigned a schema that defines what content can be saved to those structure items.
